source.en: Blaser, Magdalena "Myths of the Cofán people"

sentences.text: Tayopi tsu canse fae tsandie panzambi ni fae con'sima panza'ma'sia.
Fae a'ta tsampini japa opa consima andeni dyai'choma attepa tise ufacco'ccoi'ccu ufa.
Tsa'ma tsu de'jiambi.
Tsa'caen con'sima cachaipa fi'ttiye oshambipa asi'ttaen jayi tsaoningae.
Tsai'mbi'tssi seje'ccove u'fa'a'qque fi'ttimbi ni fae con'sime.
Tsomba me'cco jayi'ni a'choja seyo'je.
Tsonsi tsa panzambija tise ufacco'ccoma isupa ja a'choma ufaye.
Tsa'ma tise pan ufaye napisi a'choja a'tu'fa.
Tsa'caen a'tu'fasi ansundepa gi pporotsse attepa ufaya qquen in'jan.
Tsa'caen in'jamba ansundepa napi achondeccu pporotsse.
Pporotsse napipa achondeccuma attepa ufaye tson'jemba a'indeccuve atte.
Tsendeccuja tisu'pa tsa'oni dyai'fa.
Tsa'caen tise atte'ninda a'cho'qque a'i ansundeji'choma atte'fa.
Panza'suja ñotsse camba attte gringoa'candeqquia've.
Cu'a sacoma ondiccupa botaemba ondiccucho'choma.
Achondeccuja a'i napi'fa'choma attepa avujapa iñajampaña'fa.
¿Jongoesuve qui injenge'fa tsambi'ta jongoesuma qui i'fa?
Ansunde gi andeccune ufaye oshambi'pa.
Tsonsi a'choja sombopa shonquendipa faesuma mandapa su: Suya cuintsu can'niñe, can'nimba ccumbama shonchhan'giye.
Tson'jeni tise onque'ngeja andeccuni ronda'je.
Tson'ni tise yayaja a'cho tsa'onga ansundepa can'ni.
Tseni can'nimba atte a'cho ccumbama shonchhhan'jen'choma.
Tise ottaen'jencconi tsai'mbi'tssi ccumba suvaen'cco sheque'fa.
Tsonsi su: Jen'da afe'se ña shon'chhañe java enttinge'suma.
Qquen susi achoquitsa'yeja afepa tise shon'chhan nanisi su: Ja'ñonda qui panzaye oshaya.
Tsa'caen supa manda faefayi'ccoe seje'ccoeñe.
Tsomba ccattufayi'ccoi'ccu uta cañe con'sima.
Tsomba fae'ccoma ñanga afeja.
Tsa'caen susi tise yayaja andepa tise tsaosini ja.
Acho tsa'oja giyatssipa chhariccotssia.
Quini'jin ttembaja tise'pa tsa'o tsu.
Tise'ja ansundepa a'choma fi'ttiye in'jan, tsa'ma tsa'caen in'jamba ansundepa atte a'ia'caen ccumba suvaen'ccoma shonchhan'jen'choma.
Tsa'caen dapa ccaqui a'ta sombopa tsampini jayipa atte a'choveyL Tsomba in'jan mincomba tsu a'ive attiamba ja'ñojan a'chove attian, Qquen in'jan'ma tsa a'choma uta.
Tsa'caen ufapa ccoanifae a'chove fi'tti.
Toya'caen fae uttetsu, fae saquirama'qque fi'ttipa avujatsse pa'ccoma andupa tsaoni ja.
Qquen tsu tsa a'ija ccumbama shon'chhamba panza'yetssia've dapa osha'cho con'sima panzaye ashaen.
Qquen tsu tayopija osha'cho con'sima panzaye atesu'fa.
Tsonsi tise onque'ngeja su: ¿Ma'caen qui ja'ñojan fi'ttiye osha?
Tsonsi tise yayaja su: Quitsa tsu ccumbama afesi gi tsama shon'chhamba ja'ñojan panzaye osha.
Tsonsi tise onque'ngeja iñajampañamba su: ¿Majan tsu quitsaja?
Acho quitsa, qquen supa tsaoni ja'fa aña'choma panzapa.
Tsonsi tise pusheja tsama attepa tise onque'ngema iñajampañamba su: ¿Ma'caen tsu yayaja panzaye atesu?
Tsonsi condapa su: Quitsa tsu ccumbama afesi tsama shon'chhamba fi'ttiye'ja atesuya.
